high_descs: Go forward to the couch, then turn left and move forward, then turn left to face the coffee table.
Pick up the watch on the coffee table.
Turn left, step forward, then turn left to face the couch.
Put the watch in the box on the couch.
Pick up the box from the couch.
Turn left, go forward, turn left at the end of the coffee table, then go straight to the round table.
Put the box on the round table.
anns.task_desc: Put a box with a watch in it on the table.

high_descs: Walk straight then turn left at the red sofa and then left again to face the coffee table
Pick up the watch from the middle of the coffee table
Turn around and face the red sofa with the box on the seat cushion
Place the watch inside the box on the sofa cushion
Pick up the box with the watch inside from the red sofa
Turn left and walk straight then turn left at the grey sofa and walk straight to the round table
Place the box on the round table top
anns.task_desc: Have a watch inside a box on the round table

high_descs: Walk over to the coffee table.
Pick up the watch off of the coffee table.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn left to face the red couch.
Put the watch in the cardboard box that is on the seat of the couch.
Pick up the cardboard box with the watch in it off of the couch.
Turn left and walk around the coffee table to the round table in the corner of the room.
Put the cardboard box with the watch in it on the round table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cardboard box with a watch in it on the table.
